Fit In			KEY:Opportunist ~ Fit In			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OpportunistClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary									DESC:You have mastered the art of sending out nonverbal cues that suggest agreement and affiliation. This enables you to act as if you belong in any situation, whether an aristocratic garden party or an evil cult's inner sanctum. You can make a Disguise check in lieu of a Diplomacy check to influence the initial attitudes of NPCs. You do not need to change your appearance to make this check. If multiple creatures with differing views of appropriate behavior are present, you cannot simultaneously affect them and must choose a target creature or group to influence.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.29
Opportunity Attacker	KEY:Opportunist ~ Opportunity Attacker	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:OpportunistClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary									DESC:You have mastered the art of striking foes when they are at their most vulnerable. When making an attack of opportunity, you deal your sneak attack damage even if your target is not flat-footed or otherwise denied its Dexterity bonus to AC.
